I want to take over the investigation of this case.

00:42:37.370 --> 00:42:40.100
Let me find my father's murderer and clean my name.

00:42:41.060 --> 00:42:41.710
Fu Sheng,

00:42:41.710 --> 00:42:43.700
you already pleaded guilty.

00:42:44.440 --> 00:42:45.270
Guards!

00:42:45.440 --> 00:42:46.170
Yes!

00:42:46.280 --> 00:42:47.750
Get Fu Sheng to sign the confession.

00:42:48.640 --> 00:42:49.440
Hold on!

00:42:50.470 --> 00:42:51.780
Details of this case are not clear.

00:42:52.030 --> 00:42:53.620
How can you give your judgment in haste?

00:42:54.630 --> 00:42:57.060
Giving Fu Sheng the access to the investigation

00:42:57.260 --> 00:42:58.740
is against the rules, my lord.

00:42:59.190 --> 00:42:59.990
My lord,

