Second, my father is a victim.

00:43:28.080 --> 00:43:29.160
As his son,

00:43:29.270 --> 00:43:31.640
I'm obligated to find the murderer and revenge my father.

00:43:32.160 --> 00:43:33.270
Third,

00:43:33.800 --> 00:43:35.360
and this is the most important one,

